# YouTube Community Manager Agent

**A production-ready LangGraph agent for automated YouTube channel engagement**

The YouTube Community Manager Agent logs into YouTube with your credentials, navigates to a **specific target channel** you configure, opens that channel's **latest video**, and then analyzes comments, generates AI replies, builds PDF reports, and emails summaries — all through a LangGraph workflow with Playwright browser automation.

| | |
|---|---|
| **Author** | Muhammad Qasim Shabbir |
| **Email** | [muhammadqasimshabbir3@gmail.com](mailto:muhammadqasimshabbir3@gmail.com) |
